The paper discusses a mechanism for checkpoint-restart of virtual machines, which is a topic related to operating systems (cs.OS). The paper also mentions the use of plugins and user-space checkpoint-restart packages, which are topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the use of kernel driver APIs and code development, which are topics related to programming languages (cs.PL) and architecture (cs.AR).
